SELECT `cases`.*,`cases`.`id` AS `cases_id`,`cases`.`title` AS `cases_title`,`cases`.`estimate` AS `cases_estimate`,`cases`.`refs` AS `cases_refs`,`sections`.`name` AS `cases_section_name`
FROM `cases`
JOIN `sections` ON cases.section_id = sections.id
WHERE (`cases`.`is_deleted` = 0) AND (`sections`.`suite_id` = 2)
ORDER BY `sections`.`display_order`, `cases`.`display_order`
LIMIT 0,500
